com.ihealth.communication.control

Interface AbiProfile


  • public interface AbiProfile
    Public APIs for the Bp serials device profiles

    Clients need to calliHealthDevicesManager#registerClient register. When new data from Bp device, The CallbackiHealthDevicesCallback#onDeviceNotify can be triggered should call.
